# ─── Entry 20260317-023 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
entry_id: 20260317-023
timestamp: "2026-03-18T00:20:00.000Z"
session_date: 2026-03-17
interaction_type: fix
phase: build
importance: high
status: resolved
objective: Fix 3 bugs reported after game screen first build
interaction:
  user_prompt: "archive all the bugs i requested to correct since last time we archived"
  assistant_response_summary: |
    Bug 1 — Timer is per-turn not per-game: Rewrote gameStore to remove per-player timeLeftMs Record. Now tracks only turnStartedAt + clockSeconds. On each move, clock resets to full for the next player. Inactive player panel shows full clock (e.g. 0:30 static). timerBarFill now accepts clockSeconds prop and computes fill ratio correctly.
    Bug 2 — Board labels removed + bigger board: Stripped rank (left) and file (bottom) labels entirely from Board component. Freed 20px of horizontal space. Updated cellSize formula from (width-80)/8 to (width-60)/8, gaining ~2-3px per cell. Board is now larger and cleaner.
    Bug 3 — Occupied square shows wrong color: Piece's current square was inheriting the claimed color (purple/yellow). Fixed cellBg() to always return the alternating board color (cellLight/cellDark) when a piece occupies the cell, regardless of ownership. Claimed color only shows on squares the piece has left behind.
tooling:
  tools_used[2]: Edit,Write
  files_touched[4]: apps/app/stores/gameStore.ts,apps/app/components/Board.tsx,apps/app/components/PlayerPanel.tsx,apps/app/app/game/[gameId].tsx
  artifacts[1]: 014_game-screen-app-v2_app-screenshot.jpg
tags:
